ZH: 我们计划投资一只基金来实现财务目标。
EN: We plan to invest in a fund to achieve our financial goals.

ZH: 基金经理需要不断监控投资组合的表现。
EN: Fund managers need to constantly monitor the performance of the investment portfolio.

ZH: 把一部分资产放入基金可以有效分散风险。
EN: Putting some assets into a fund can effectively diversify risk.

ZH: 基金的收益通常比存款利率高。
EN: The return on funds is usually higher than deposit rates.

ZH: 基金投资有风险，投资需谨慎。
EN: Fund investment carries risks, so investment should be cautious.

ZH: 我们的基金经理有丰富的投资经验。
EN: Our fund manager has extensive investment experience.

ZH: 基金投资是投资市场中的一种常见方式。
EN: Fund investment is a common way in the investment market.

ZH: 基金公司通常管理多个基金产品。
EN: Fund companies typically manage multiple fund products.

ZH: 风险投资基金投资创新企业。
EN: Venture capital funds invest in innovative companies.

ZH: 基金的份额可以在二级市场进行买卖。
EN: Fund shares can be bought and sold in the secondary market.

ZH: 基金定投有助于长期均衡投资。
EN: Fund regular investment helps maintain long-term balanced investment.

ZH: 基金行业的监管日益加强。
EN: Regulation of the fund industry is becoming increasingly stringent.

ZH: 基金公司必须定期公布基金的净值。
EN: Fund companies must regularly disclose the net asset value of the funds.

ZH: 政府设立了基金来支持特定领域的发展。
EN: The government has set up funds to support the development of specific sectors.

ZH: 基金经理需要根据市场行情灵活调整投资组合。
EN: Fund managers need to adjust investment portfolios flexibly according to market conditions.

ZH: 投资基金的运作需要严格遵守法律法规。
EN: The operation of investment funds needs to strictly adhere to laws and regulations.

ZH: 基金的风险收益比需根据投资者风险偏好来选择。
EN: The risk-return ratio of funds should be selected based on investor risk preferences.

ZH: 基金的申购和赎回需要遵守规定的时间和流程。
EN: The subscription and redemption of funds need to adhere to the specified time and procedures.

ZH: 基金公司会定期向投资者报告基金的运作情况。
EN: Fund companies regularly report the operation of funds to investors.
